<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57889">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57889">
Endemic species of southern France, recently reported in Italy (
<bibRefCitation author="Bardiani, M" journalOrPublisher="Bollettino dell'Associazione Romana di Entomologia." pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" pagination="69 - 90" refId="B6009114" refString="Bardiani, M, Buzzetti, FM, 2009. Blattari e Ortotteri delle Riserve Naturali &quot;Agoraie di sopra e Moggeto&quot; (Liguria, Genova) e &quot;Guadine Pradaccio&quot; (Emilia-Romagna, Parma) (Blattaria, Orthoptera). Bollettino dell'Associazione Romana di Entomologia. 64: 69 - 90" title="Blattari e Ortotteri delle Riserve Naturali &quot; Agoraie di sopra e Moggeto &quot; (Liguria, Genova) e &quot; Guadine Pradaccio &quot; (Emilia-Romagna, Parma) (Blattaria, Orthoptera)" volume="64" year="2009">Bardiani and Buzzetti 2009</bibRefCitation>
). A review of the genus is underway (
<bibRefCitation author="Iorio, C." journalOrPublisher="WBA Handbooks 10, Verona: 1 - 579" pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" refId="B6232886" refString="Iorio, C., Scherini, R., Fontana, P., Buzzetti, F. M., Kleukers, R., Ode, B., Massa, B., 2019. Grasshoppers &amp; Crickets of Italy. A photographic field guide to all the species. WBA Handbooks 10, Verona: 1-579" title="Grasshoppers &amp; Crickets of Italy. A photographic field guide to all the species" year="2019">Iorio et al. 2019</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57889">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57889">
In France, it lives in wet meadows and along the edges of streams. In Italy, it is reported as a mountain and hygrophilous species. It lives in wet grasslands, in dense vegetation. The adults can be found in summer and autumn (
<bibRefCitation author="Massa, B" journalOrPublisher="Calderini-Edizioni" pageId="0" pageNumber="57889" refId="B6007852" refString="Massa, B, Fontana, P, Buzzeti, FM, Kleukers, R, Ode, B, 2012. Fauna d'Italia: Orthoptera. Calderini-Edizioni" title="Fauna d'Italia: Orthoptera" year="2012">Massa et al. 2012</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
